Based on Day 1 (today) training.  Below is the assignment for you all.  Complete it before Day 2 session.

Create console application called "ITGTraining24" using .Net Framework in Visual Studio
Create sample class called "MyFirstClass" and try to add any external packages from NuGet like SQL/Azure etc.,
In the above Class, declare string variable
Assign any text to the variable and display it as output ,using console class
Clean and build the application (make sure build is good without any errors)
Run the application to see the string variable value in the out put console


using System;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Linq;
using System.Text;
using System.Threading.Tasks;

namespace ITGTraining24
{
    class Program
    {
        public string str;
        public int age;
    }
}

using System;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Linq;
using System.Text;
using System.Threading.Tasks;

namespace ITGTraining24
{
    class MyFirstClass
    {
        static void Main(string[] args)
        {
            Program obj = new Program();
            Console.WriteLine("Enter your Input");
            obj.str = Console.ReadLine();
            Console.WriteLine(obj.str);
        }
    }
}
